title: Hitlists searchable (updated, by request)
description:
Can't recall who requested this - STFMaryville, maybe? Regardless, here it is and, for those of you unfamiliar with "Hitlists", read on...


Hitlist breakdowns

Every week TPB member, shipjolly, uploads several torrents called "Hitlists". These torrents represent everything that was scanned for that particular week: current, old and OOP. I've found these to be very, VERY helpful in plugging holes in my collection.

This torrent is an easily searchable .rtf file I created that lists the contents of each of these torrents available on TPB, excluding his separate 'Hitlist Adult' and 'Hitlist Non-English' uploads, from 4/11/12 thru 8/28/13, making it current as of this writing. 

To find these torrents, search for "Hitlist" under "Other", download what you need and pay it forward by seeding for a spell. 

Now everyone say, "Thank you, shipjolly!"
